  "text": "Theorem 5.2 (Theorem 3.3 of [CITATION_1] ). For T \u2208 R m\u00d7n a binary preference matrix, S a (\u03b3 , \u03b6 )-typical set of users, and a matrixT satisfying \u2225T \u2212T \u2225 F \u2264 \u03b5 \u2225T \u2225 F , for a chosen parameter \u03c8 \u2208 (0, 1 \u2212 \u03b6 ) there exists some S \u2032 \u2282 S of size at least (1 \u2212 \u03c8 \u2212 \u03b6 )m such that",
